1. *On* je već *zauzet* (He is already taken).
2. *Zauzela* je svoj stav (She took her stance).
3. *Zauzme* li on drugo mišljenje? (Will he take another opinion?)
4. *Zauzeti* stav prema nečemu (To take a stance towards something).
5. Ona je *zauzeta* za svoju porodicu (She is devoted to her family).